Text: RE Taite Zapalac Welcome To The WorldCharlie Except for Enron Recruiting has gone very well I guess you cant win them all I am waiting for one more offer before I make a decision I will most likely end up in Houston back at El Paso If I end up back in Houston we should grab lunch a couple of times Keep in touch Original Message From mailto Sent Monday November AM To Will Zapalac Subject Re Taite Zapalac Welcome To The World Congratualtions Will May God bless you and your family Shes a beautiful baby How is recruiting going Any idea where you think you will end up Im sorry it did not work out at Enron I know that you will do well wherever you go Charlie
